I'm using exabgp in a DNS resolver anycasting setup with ipv4 and ipv6 prefixes. everything seems to be working as expected but my log gets spammed with "the route family is not configured on neighbor":

```
Wed, 01 Jun 2016 08:56:32 | ERROR    | 1744   | configuration | the route family is not configured on neighbor
Wed, 01 Jun 2016 08:56:32 | ERROR    | 1744   | configuration | the route family is not configured on neighbor
Wed, 01 Jun 2016 08:56:32 | ERROR    | 1744   | configuration | the route family is not configured on neighbor
