Wed, 01 Jun 2016 08:56:35 | ERROR    | 1744   | configuration | the route family is not configured on neighbor
Wed, 01 Jun 2016 08:56:35 | ERROR    | 1744   | configuration | the route family is not configured on neighbor
```

it seems like this message appears for each "announce" command, exabgp gets from my "health-check" ruby script process. 

here is my config:
```
